@startuml
title Gambar 5.15 Sequence Diagram Login

actor User
participant "Login Page" as LoginPage
participant "Auth API" as AuthAPI
database "User Model" as UserModel
participant "JWT Service" as JWT

User -> LoginPage: Mengisi username dan password
LoginPage -> AuthAPI: POST /api/auth/login
AuthAPI -> UserModel: Mencari user berdasarkan username
UserModel --> AuthAPI: Data user
AuthAPI -> AuthAPI: Validasi password dan status akun

alt MFA aktif
  AuthAPI --> LoginPage: Meminta kode MFA
  User -> LoginPage: Mengisi kode MFA
  LoginPage -> AuthAPI: POST /api/auth/mfa/verify
end

AuthAPI -> JWT: Membuat token
JWT --> AuthAPI: Token
AuthAPI --> LoginPage: Data user dan token
LoginPage --> User: Dashboard sesuai role

@enduml
